      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WORDS OF WISDOM (6) had a tricky draw and ran well to finish second, beaten 1.75 lengths, (20.13) at this track. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Well placed and gets her chance. BURNSIDE MATT (2) goes very well over this trip including three wins. Below best last time at this track (20.49) in a Grade 5, finishing a 8 length sixth. Looks well placed here and among the chances. ALOHA NORMA (1) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when fifth at Casino over 300m behind Jimary Freedom (17.96) in a Grade 5. Scored at her previous run. One of the main contenders. OUR MIRACLES (3) is a last-start placegetter who should be thereabouts.",
